OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1776791154
OL,3,CCarlisle United fan completes solo-
OL,4,Ccycle to Truro to raise funds for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FA Carlisle United fan has completed a
OL,8,Fgruelling 500-mile cycle ride to Truro
OL,9,Fto watch the Blues final away match of
OL,10,Fthe National League season.
OL,12,F61-year-old Graham Moss set off from
OL,13,FCarlisle on Monday and landed in the
OL,14,FCornish city on Friday after
OL,15,Fcompleting around 100 miles each day
OL,16,Fon his bike whilst being on his own.
OL,18,FHe completed the solo, unsupported
OL,19,Fcycle to watch the match and also has
OL,20,Fraised several thousand pounds for
OL,21,FProstate Cancer UK along the way.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1776791154
OL,3,CCarlisle United fan completes solo-
OL,4,Ccycle to Truro to raise funds for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV Border Graham said:
OL,8,F"It really was because the opportunity
OL,9,Fwas there and because I could.
OL,11,F"I am a very keen cyclist and I do
OL,12,Fprobably about 11,000 miles a year on
OL,13,Fthe bike.
OL,15,F"Three years ago when Carlisle won the
OL,16,Fplayoff final at Wembley I cycled down
OL,17,Ffor that and when the fixtures came
OL,18,Fout at the start of this season a few
OL,19,Fpeople suggested that I did Truro.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1776791154
OL,3,CCarlisle United fan completes solo-
OL,4,Ccycle to Truro to raise funds for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,F"The fixture finally came up but I
OL,8,Fcouldn't get a ticket for it but just
OL,9,Fabout a week before the match I
OL,10,Fmanaged to get my hands on one and
OL,11,Fthought let's just do it."
OL,13,FDespite being such an avid cyclist
OL,14,Fthere was an extra special personal
OL,15,Felement to completing the challenge
OL,16,Ffor Graham.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1776791154
OL,3,CCarlisle United fan completes solo-
OL,4,Ccycle to Truro to raise funds for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FHe said: "I was just going to do it as
OL,8,Fa personal challenge but then thought
OL,9,Fwhy not raise some money for Prostate
OL,10,FCancer UK because a few people I know
OL,11,Fare affected by prostate cancer and it
OL,12,Fis a very deserving cause.
OL,14,F"I also did it in memory of my dad, I
OL,15,Flost him in January and he was very
OL,16,Fmuch in my thoughts and the
OL,17,Finspiration behind doing it.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1776791154
OL,3,CCarlisle United fan completes solo-
OL,4,Ccycle to Truro to raise funds for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,F"The challenge was between 460 and 500
OL,8,Fmiles with around 100 miles done each
OL,9,Fday. The weather on two of the days
OL,10,Fwas horrific with monsoon like rain
OL,11,Fcoming down on the Wednesday and the
OL,12,Flast day as well. I was pleased to get
OL,13,Fthere in the end and the legs were a
OL,14,Fbit tired."
OL,16,FGraham said that on two of the five
OL,17,Fdays he faced fierce weather
OL,18,Fconditions but even a cosy country pub
OL,19,Fcould not stop him from going all the
OL,20,Fway to Cornwall.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1776791154
OL,3,CCarlisle United fan completes solo-
OL,4,Ccycle to Truro to raise funds for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FHe said: "About half way through I was
OL,8,Fsoaked through and found a lovely
OL,9,Fquiet pub that had a fire roaring in
OL,10,Fit to dry off. I was having a laugh
OL,11,Fand a pint with the locals and could
OL,12,Fhave just stayed there happily but
OL,13,Fthought to myself that I had to finish
OL,14,Fit, there are another 60 miles to go."
OL,16,FDespite facing challenges with the
OL,17,Fweather Graham said that the people he
OL,18,Fmet along the way made the experience
OL,19,Fspecial.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1776791154
OL,3,CCarlisle United fan completes solo-
OL,4,Ccycle to Truro to raise funds for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FHe said: "The best bit of it all was
OL,8,Fthe people. I had people putting me up
OL,9,Ffor a night on the way down who I had
OL,10,Fnever met before. I put the word out
OL,11,Fthere on social media for what I was
OL,12,Fdoing and even had two offers for the
OL,13,Ffirst night for where to stay.
OL,15,F"I don't think anyone is going to
OL,16,Fpretend it was the greatest of matches
OL,17,Fbut the number of fans that we took
OL,18,Fwas amazing.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1776791154
OL,3,CCarlisle United fan completes solo-
OL,4,Ccycle to Truro to raise funds for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,F"I support both Carlisle and
OL,8,FWorkington Reds and seeing Workington
OL,9,Fwin to keep their survival in the
OL,10,Fleague was brilliant."
OL,12,FWith Carlisle United now having
OL,13,Fsecured third place in the National
OL,14,FLeague and a play-off semi-final
OL,15,Flooming, the prospect of another trip
OL,16,Fto Wembley could be on the cards.
OL,18,FGraham says that his mind has already
OL,19,Fturned to the potential cycle to the
OL,20,Fcapital.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/9
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1776791154
OL,3,CCarlisle United fan completes solo-
OL,4,Ccycle to Truro to raise funds for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FHe said: "I am certainly considering
OL,8,Fcycling down to Wembley again if
OL,9,FCarlisle get to the final, it
OL,10,Fcertainly will be a lot easier than
OL,11,Fwhat cycling to Truro was."
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
